WEBVTT

00:00.668 --> 00:05.070
Hello, Dr. Bowman.
It's good to see you again.

00:05.072 --> 00:07.706
I've been waiting
to ask you stuff all week.

00:07.708 --> 00:09.408
That's why I'm here,
Dwight --

00:09.410 --> 00:11.010
to answer
your questions.

00:11.012 --> 00:14.113
We've turned the tables
a little, haven't we?

00:14.115 --> 00:16.115
I wonder
if I'm about to learn

00:16.117 --> 00:18.484
as much about your life
as you did about mine.

00:18.486 --> 00:20.419
Rosen:
Your honor, I object.

00:20.421 --> 00:22.755
The defendant
cannot treat the witness

00:22.757 --> 00:24.423
as if he were at an appointment
with his therapist.

00:24.425 --> 00:26.025
Richwood: Yes.

00:26.027 --> 00:26.725
Mr. Darnell?

00:26.727 --> 00:28.460
Dr. Bowman is present

00:28.462 --> 00:31.230
to speak in his capacity
as a psychologist.

00:31.232 --> 00:34.099
More specifically, to render
his analysis of my mental --

00:34.101 --> 00:35.667
Objection sustained.

00:35.669 --> 00:39.204
Mr. Darnell, since you insist
as acting as your own attorney,

00:39.206 --> 00:41.407
I continue
to give you leeway,

00:41.409 --> 00:44.343
but once again,
I urge you to consult

00:44.345 --> 00:45.978
with your court-appointed
attorney for advice.

00:45.980 --> 00:47.312
He's right there.

00:47.314 --> 00:49.381
Taylor: If he
gives the game away here,

00:49.383 --> 00:53.085
maybe he'll be arrogant enough
to answer some questions

00:53.087 --> 00:56.021
about his Nazi friends
when court adjourns.

00:56.023 --> 00:58.524
Tell us who
his Aryan shot-caller is.

00:58.526 --> 01:01.493
During their investigation,
the Pasadena police --

01:01.495 --> 01:04.897
they asked
for Dr. Bowman's services

01:04.899 --> 01:09.601
in order that "through analyzing
the methodology

01:09.603 --> 01:12.404
and potential motives
of these homicides

01:12.406 --> 01:16.175
to locate and/or identify
a suspect."

01:16.177 --> 01:17.776
Is this
an accurate description

01:17.778 --> 01:19.478
of the job that you were asked
to perform, Dr. Bowman?

01:19.480 --> 01:22.748
In brief, yes.
Huh.

01:22.750 --> 01:25.617
So, before we met
at the behest of detectives,

01:25.619 --> 01:28.153
you had compiled
an imaginary portrait

01:28.155 --> 01:30.122
of my -- my --
my upbringing?

01:30.124 --> 01:31.356
My character?

01:31.358 --> 01:34.326
I speculated
on your personality.

01:34.328 --> 01:35.994
By lumping me in
with a lot of other people?

01:35.996 --> 01:38.497
Not a lot of other<i> people,</i>
Dwight.

01:38.499 --> 01:40.666
A lot
of other<i> murderers.</i>

01:41.802 --> 01:46.038
It is my understanding that
the word "murder" or "homicide"

01:46.040 --> 01:48.707
is reserved
for the unlawful killing

01:48.709 --> 01:50.142
of other human beings.

01:50.144 --> 01:53.612
My so-called victims
were either involved with

01:53.614 --> 01:56.815
or already were part of
an inferior race,

01:56.817 --> 01:59.618
and therefore,
it is my defense --
Objection!

01:59.620 --> 02:02.321
The 6 adults
and 2 children under 10

02:02.323 --> 02:04.223
shot to death
by the defendant

02:04.225 --> 02:06.658
were human
in every sense of the word.

02:06.660 --> 02:07.860
Richwood: Sustained.

02:07.862 --> 02:09.895
Claiming your victims
were unworthy of life

02:09.897 --> 02:12.631
because they were minorities
is not a defense, Mr. Darnell.

02:12.633 --> 02:14.433
Make your point,
if you have one.

02:14.435 --> 02:15.501
I do.

02:15.503 --> 02:17.970
Dr. Bowman,
am I correct in stating

02:17.972 --> 02:20.639
that on July 16th
of last year,

02:20.641 --> 02:22.541
you predicted
that I would be

02:22.543 --> 02:24.643
at one of 12 addresses
in Pasadena

02:24.645 --> 02:27.980
using this gun
to execute a married couple

02:27.982 --> 02:32.284
who was intent on diluting
the purity of the white race?

02:32.286 --> 02:34.620
We narrowed down the date
and some potential targets

02:34.622 --> 02:36.855
in such a way to affect
your arrest if that's --

02:36.857 --> 02:40.626
So, I stand here today
on trial for my life,

02:40.628 --> 02:44.396
partly because
you took my individual nature

02:44.398 --> 02:47.733
and reduced it
to a pattern?

02:47.735 --> 02:52.671
You shrunk it down
to fit a generic profile?

02:52.673 --> 02:54.540
That's one way
of looking at it.

02:54.542 --> 02:56.542
What other possible way
could I look at it, Doctor?

02:56.544 --> 02:59.244
Well, one might also say
that in the final analysis,

02:59.246 --> 03:01.280
you just weren't
very original.

03:01.282 --> 03:05.717
♪♪

03:08.155 --> 03:11.623
Well, Doctor,
since I'm so obvious,

03:11.625 --> 03:14.826
maybe you could
offer the court

03:14.828 --> 03:17.563
an illustration
of your predictive powers.

03:17.565 --> 03:19.431
For example,
could you reveal

03:19.433 --> 03:22.367
to the ladies and gentlemen
of the jury

03:22.369 --> 03:26.038
what I'm about to do in, say,
the next 10 seconds?

03:26.040 --> 03:30.509
♪♪

03:40.721 --> 03:42.120
[ Gasping ]

03:42.122 --> 03:43.622
[ Screaming ]

03:43.624 --> 03:45.624
Get down!
Get down!

03:48.829 --> 03:50.696
Woman: Get down, get down!
Get down, get down!

03:52.900 --> 03:54.399
Move, move!

03:55.970 --> 03:57.936
[ Gunshot ]

04:04.345 --> 04:06.311
[ Gasps ]

04:06.313 --> 04:10.482
♪♪

04:12.753 --> 04:15.254
Stay with me, Chief,
stay with me.

04:15.256 --> 04:19.891
♪♪

04:26.200 --> 04:27.499
[ Elevator bell dings ]

04:27.501 --> 04:31.603
[ Indistinct shouting ]

04:33.374 --> 04:36.208
Woman: Excuse us.

04:36.210 --> 04:37.609
Excuse us.
Lieutenant Provenza,

04:37.611 --> 04:39.044
how many people were shot
in the courtroom?

04:39.046 --> 04:40.846
Can you confirm the death
of Dwight Darnell?

04:40.848 --> 04:43.282
Can you tell us why the
courthouse has been blocked off?

04:43.284 --> 04:44.583
Are there more threats?

04:44.585 --> 04:46.418
Why is the LAPD
investigating the shooting

04:46.420 --> 04:48.020
instead of
the sheriff's office?

04:48.022 --> 04:51.223
'Cause the sheriff's office
has conflicts in this case.

04:51.225 --> 04:53.825
What conflicts?
They're called bullets.
Excuse me.

04:53.827 --> 04:56.428
So, is this an ethical
or a criminal investigation?

04:56.430 --> 04:59.364
Yes.
[ Indistinct shouting ]

04:59.366 --> 05:01.900
♪♪

05:01.902 --> 05:03.802
Flynn: All right.
Richwood: To begin with,

05:03.804 --> 05:07.172
I can keep the jurors
sequestered and give
you their identities.

05:07.174 --> 05:08.840
Sharon:
That might help.

05:08.842 --> 05:10.742
Flynn: We'll also need a list
of all the clerks and deputies

05:10.744 --> 05:12.511
who had access
to the evidence,

05:12.513 --> 05:14.413
because what happened here today
just wasn't a mass shooting.

05:14.415 --> 05:16.982
It had to be
a conspiracy.

05:16.984 --> 05:18.950
Dwight probably won't live,
but we'll see.

05:18.952 --> 05:20.385
What about Dr. Joe?

05:20.387 --> 05:22.788
It's 50/50.

05:24.158 --> 05:25.691
I'm...

05:26.493 --> 05:29.895
I am very sorry
about Chief Taylor.

05:29.897 --> 05:32.264
♪♪

05:32.266 --> 05:34.166
He was a cop's cop.

05:34.168 --> 05:35.467
♪♪

05:35.469 --> 05:37.235
Never more than today.

05:37.237 --> 05:39.071
And DDA Rosen,
too.

05:39.073 --> 05:41.540
God,
I don't believe it.

05:41.542 --> 05:42.908
I'm gonna get
your prelim started

05:42.910 --> 05:44.976
so you don't have to
come to the morgue, okay?

05:44.978 --> 05:46.211
Your honor?

05:46.213 --> 05:49.481
Any idea how that gun
could have been loaded?

05:49.483 --> 05:52.751
Richwood: No, the disabling wire
is checked always

05:52.753 --> 05:55.687
before it comes into court
by both the DDA and the deputy.

05:55.689 --> 05:57.422
The wire was clipped.

05:57.424 --> 05:59.257
All Dwight had to do
was pull it out,

05:59.259 --> 06:00.792
which he could have done
through the bag.

06:00.794 --> 06:02.828
That's what I looked like
from where I was sitting.

06:02.830 --> 06:04.429
Maybe Deputy Simms
and Rosen

06:04.431 --> 06:06.431
just did a visual check
of the wire, sir.

06:06.433 --> 06:08.100
Wouldn't be unusual.

06:08.102 --> 06:09.801
Flynn: It's hard to believe
they had anything to do

06:09.803 --> 06:12.371
with the conspiracy
since they both ended up dead.

06:12.373 --> 06:13.739
Hey, Sharon?

06:13.741 --> 06:15.574
Would you like to wait
in the judge's chambers?

06:15.576 --> 06:17.075
I'm sure his honor
wouldn't mind?

06:17.077 --> 06:18.443
No, I'm good,
Andy.

06:18.445 --> 06:20.979
I should stay
with the scene of my action.

06:20.981 --> 06:23.014
Oh, uh, Sharon,
the spectators

06:23.016 --> 06:25.117
and the reporters
that were present?

06:25.119 --> 06:28.120
Should I continue to have
the deputies hold them, too,

06:28.122 --> 06:29.621
or --
or let them go?

06:29.623 --> 06:33.458
Uh, Captain, I can't believe
I'm about to say this.

06:33.460 --> 06:35.761
Uh, but according
to the rules --

06:35.763 --> 06:37.929
uh,
written by you --
Sharon: I know.

06:37.931 --> 06:39.931
I used my firearm,
so I have to wait

06:39.933 --> 06:42.033
until Force investigation
interviews me

06:42.035 --> 06:44.569
before I can actively continue
with this case.

06:44.571 --> 06:45.971
Yes,
but that doesn't mean

06:45.973 --> 06:47.706
that we can't talk about it
in front of you

06:47.708 --> 06:49.274
or you ask questions
if you want.

06:49.276 --> 06:53.044
We will see the jurors
and the people from the gallery

06:53.046 --> 06:54.713
in just a few minutes,
your honor.

06:54.715 --> 06:56.848
I'll let them know,
Lieutenant.
Thank you.

06:58.051 --> 07:00.886
♪♪

07:02.423 --> 07:09.661
Before we go on,
this is a lousy day.

07:09.663 --> 07:12.597
I'm feeling
pretty upset myself.

07:12.599 --> 07:15.066
So, if anyone needs a break

07:15.068 --> 07:20.372
before we start figuring out who
put this conspiracy together,

07:20.374 --> 07:24.509
it would be
completely understood.

07:24.511 --> 07:28.747
♪♪

07:30.083 --> 07:31.750
Good.

07:31.752 --> 07:32.851
Mike?

07:32.853 --> 07:35.821
No prints on the clip
or the remaining bullet.

07:35.823 --> 07:37.222
Amy?

07:37.224 --> 07:38.657
After
the shooting started,

07:38.659 --> 07:40.459
Deputy Simms tried
to activate Dwight's stun belt,

07:40.461 --> 07:41.860
but the controls
are jammed.

07:41.862 --> 07:44.362
That's why Simms was too late
drawing his side arm.

07:44.364 --> 07:46.097
He tried
to shock Dwight first.

07:46.099 --> 07:47.866
Well,
if Dwight's plan

07:47.868 --> 07:49.835
was to kill
as many people as possible,

07:49.837 --> 07:51.837
he should have shot
the deputy first.

07:51.839 --> 07:55.807
Unless Dwight knew the stun belt
was disabled.

07:55.809 --> 07:57.642
How would he have known that,
though?

07:57.644 --> 07:58.844
That's a good question.

07:58.846 --> 08:00.745
Sharon:
Here's a few more.

08:00.747 --> 08:02.647
Who loaded
and enabled the gun?

08:02.649 --> 08:04.883
How did Dwight know
the gun was loaded?

08:04.885 --> 08:07.519
And why did he shoot
Joe Bowman first?

08:07.521 --> 08:08.753
Just a question.

08:08.755 --> 08:11.056
Well, was Dr. Joe
the primary target?

08:11.058 --> 08:13.225
Sharon:
It looks that way to me,

08:13.227 --> 08:15.160
and do you think,
for the time being,

08:15.162 --> 08:18.463
that we should let the
conspirators, whoever they are,

08:18.465 --> 08:22.567
think that Dwight succeeded
and that Dr. Joe is dead?

08:22.569 --> 08:24.069
I could help with that.

08:24.071 --> 08:25.704
Captain?
Oh.

08:25.706 --> 08:28.540
Lieutenant Camacho.

08:28.542 --> 08:31.743
This is
the, uh, weapon I fired.

08:31.745 --> 08:33.211
I'll be
just a second.

08:33.213 --> 08:37.182
Did I mention,
in addition to profiling Dwight,

08:37.184 --> 08:41.520
Dr. Joe also evaluated
his capacity to stand trial

08:41.522 --> 08:43.021
and to act
as his own attorney?

08:43.023 --> 08:47.325
I am going to speak
with FID.

08:47.327 --> 08:49.027
Thank you.

08:49.029 --> 08:50.662
I'm coming.

08:51.999 --> 08:56.768
So, there is a record of Dr. Joe
and Dwight's conversations.

08:56.770 --> 08:58.370
Covered by privilege.

08:58.372 --> 08:59.905
Well, as long
as Dwight is alive.

08:59.907 --> 09:04.676
Doctor, you're our
resident expert on the subject,

09:04.678 --> 09:06.011
so as regards
to Dr. Joe?

09:06.013 --> 09:07.546
I could report his death
to the media,

09:07.548 --> 09:09.047
but you should have
Deputy Chief Howard

09:09.049 --> 09:12.617
contact his next of kin
and warn them beforehand.

09:12.619 --> 09:15.220
These will do
as prelims.

09:15.222 --> 09:19.090
I'll call you
if any of this changes.

09:19.092 --> 09:20.392
Thank you.

09:20.394 --> 09:21.993
Mike,
why don't you look around

09:21.995 --> 09:24.529
for who had access
to Dwight Darnell's weapon?

09:24.531 --> 09:27.399
There may be
a standout.

09:27.401 --> 09:28.700
I'll see
if I can find someone

09:28.702 --> 09:31.202
with a swastika
tattooed on his forehead.

09:31.204 --> 09:35.941
Uh, Amy, make sure that Dr. Joe
is anonymous, protected,

09:35.943 --> 09:38.610
and as far as the rest
of the world knows, dead.

09:38.612 --> 09:40.211
And keep an eye
on Dwight.

09:40.213 --> 09:42.747
If he wakes up,
you need to talk to him.

09:42.749 --> 09:44.549
I'll let you know
how it goes.

09:44.551 --> 09:46.084
Buzz: Uh, Lieutenant,
you want me to grab

09:46.086 --> 09:47.786
all the video
from the courtroom?

09:47.788 --> 09:49.921
I want you to grab all the video
in the<i> courthouse.</i>

09:49.923 --> 09:51.656
Let's find out
who all was here today.

09:51.658 --> 09:53.391
Yes, sir.

09:53.393 --> 09:56.962
Julio, you need to run parole
and probation searches

09:56.964 --> 09:59.264
on every known Nazi
and skinhead.

09:59.266 --> 10:01.900
In-Include those in county,
as well.

10:01.902 --> 10:03.935
Should we start
with Henry Colson, sir?

10:03.937 --> 10:06.204
We can't rule out
what happened here

10:06.206 --> 10:09.774
as payback for how his father
and brother died last week.

10:09.776 --> 10:11.676
Yeah, good call,
good call, Julio.

10:11.678 --> 10:13.011
Oh,
and I was thinking.

10:13.013 --> 10:16.748
Um, your foster kid,
Mark --

10:16.750 --> 10:18.950
now, he lived
with the Colsons.

10:18.952 --> 10:23.221
He might be able to ID
some members of Z-Brotherhood,

10:23.223 --> 10:26.191
the ones that came to visit
when Dwight was there.

10:26.193 --> 10:27.626
I'm sorry,
sir,

10:27.628 --> 10:29.761
but Mark isn't going anywhere
near these White Power nut jobs.

10:29.763 --> 10:34.232
Julio, look, the guy who killed
Mark's mother is dead.

10:34.234 --> 10:36.935
It hasn't stopped
the violence much, sir.

10:36.937 --> 10:40.238
I'll get a removal order
for Colson,

10:40.240 --> 10:42.407
and we'll see if he had
anything to do with this.

10:42.409 --> 10:43.708
♪♪

10:43.710 --> 10:45.377
God help him
if he did.

10:45.379 --> 10:50.615
Well, I've never been
very sure about God, Andy.

10:50.617 --> 10:52.083
But today?

10:52.085 --> 10:54.986
♪♪

10:54.988 --> 11:00.225
Today,
I believe in the devil.

11:07.668 --> 11:09.734
But I can confirm
there were five deaths,

11:09.736 --> 11:14.906
including LAPD assistant chief
of operations Russell Taylor,

11:14.908 --> 11:16.841
whose position
I am temporarily filling

11:16.843 --> 11:18.843
while the LAPD finds those

11:18.845 --> 11:20.578
who aided and abetted
Dwight Darnell.

11:20.580 --> 11:22.180
I will take
a few questions.

11:22.182 --> 11:23.848
What about the report
from the coroner's office

11:23.850 --> 11:26.017
that Dr. Joe Bowman
was shot and killed

11:26.019 --> 11:28.053
while giving testimony
on the stand?

11:28.055 --> 11:30.155
I'm not going to talk about
any of the other murders

11:30.157 --> 11:31.790
until relatives
have been notified.

11:31.792 --> 11:33.091
[ Indistinct shouting ]
Yes.

11:33.093 --> 11:35.193
Last week,
the LAPD was responsible

11:35.195 --> 11:38.563
for two fatalities inside
the so-called Z-Brotherhood.

11:38.565 --> 11:40.165
Was this shooting
an attempt

11:40.167 --> 11:42.267
to get revenge
on law enforcement?

11:42.269 --> 11:43.435
I-I have no idea.

11:43.437 --> 11:47.672
Now, all we know for sure
is this was a conspiracy

11:47.674 --> 11:50.341
against the justice system
and the people who serve it,

11:50.343 --> 11:55.246
and frankly, an attack on our
common ideas of civilization.

11:55.248 --> 11:56.781
Okay, Julio.

11:56.783 --> 11:58.349
How are we doing

11:58.351 --> 12:01.720
with our parole and probation
searches of Nazi world?

12:01.722 --> 12:03.121
Not great,
sir.

12:03.123 --> 12:05.156
There's one weird thing,
and it's not the first time

12:05.158 --> 12:07.292
the Z-Brotherhood
has done something like this.

12:07.294 --> 12:09.894
Most of them live in a group
of old apartment complexes

12:09.896 --> 12:13.031
on the same city block,
and they own all the buildings.

12:13.033 --> 12:14.399
Birds of a feather?

12:14.401 --> 12:17.435
Should flock off,
preferably to another city.

12:17.437 --> 12:19.871
They do flock off, sir,
but only to other neighborhoods.

12:19.873 --> 12:21.439
The Brotherhood
causes trouble,

12:21.441 --> 12:24.275
tries to move out blacks
and Latinos around its property.

12:24.277 --> 12:26.444
Then the city steps in,
condemns the building,

12:26.446 --> 12:28.980
pays them off,
and redevelops.
Pays them off.

12:28.982 --> 12:31.282
Again, these maniacs
in a real-estate con.

12:31.284 --> 12:34.285
How come we don't know more
about these Zyklon dirtbags?

12:34.287 --> 12:36.054
Sanchez: Well, sir,
until recently,

12:36.056 --> 12:38.223
they were just everyday
drug dealers and gun runners.

12:38.225 --> 12:40.091
I mean,
they preached white power,

12:40.093 --> 12:44.129
but mostly just sold meth
in L.A. and weapons in Mexico.

12:44.131 --> 12:45.930
This particular
real-estate issue --

12:45.932 --> 12:47.599
there's nothing
really illegal about it.

12:47.601 --> 12:49.200
We should
get search warrants

12:49.202 --> 12:52.570
and tear the Brotherhoods'
apartment buildings apartment.

12:52.572 --> 12:54.939
Catch them with this
million dollars worth of weapons

12:54.941 --> 12:56.441
that are still missing.

12:56.443 --> 12:57.776
Sir,
search warrants?

12:57.778 --> 12:59.010
We'd need probable cause
for each apartment.

12:59.012 --> 13:00.678
I mean,
where's the evidence for that?

13:00.680 --> 13:04.315
Maybe all of their properties
could be condemned again, huh?

13:04.317 --> 13:05.316
Flynn?

13:05.318 --> 13:07.819
Yeah, well,
Dwight had no visitors

13:07.821 --> 13:10.288
while he was at county
awaiting trial,

13:10.290 --> 13:12.791
and he cycled
a lot of cellmates,

13:12.793 --> 13:14.492
but no skinheads
or Nazis in the bunch.

13:14.494 --> 13:16.127
Mike.

13:16.129 --> 13:18.429
The gun was only signed
into evidence a few times.

13:18.431 --> 13:21.566
Richwood's clerk, Jan Adamms,
was in charge of that.

13:21.568 --> 13:22.934
She's on her way up.

13:22.936 --> 13:24.202
Buzz: I have the video ready,
Lieutenant.

13:24.204 --> 13:27.539
Top right is
the judge's clerk, Jan.

13:27.541 --> 13:29.707
Here we go.

13:29.709 --> 13:34.179
♪♪

13:37.984 --> 13:41.719
Well, she certainly
looked surprised.

13:41.721 --> 13:45.657
♪♪

13:45.659 --> 13:48.760
Rusty:
Did he suffer?

13:48.762 --> 13:50.061
