than either of them knew.

20:16.749 --> 20:20.318
But -- but wouldn't
all of that be privileged?

20:20.320 --> 20:21.886
I mean,
how could anyone else

20:21.888 --> 20:23.854
know what they were
talking about?

20:23.856 --> 20:28.693
Yes, that is another
really good question.

20:28.695 --> 20:31.028
[ Elevator bell dings ]
