from county again

20:38.571 --> 20:40.538
after what happened to my father
and my brother,

20:40.540 --> 20:42.373
if you guys are about
to make an arrest or something,

20:42.375 --> 20:44.175
it's gonna look like
I'm telling you stuff.

20:44.177 --> 20:46.277
Sanchez: You<i> are</i> gonna tell us
stuff, Colson, or guess what?

20:46.279 --> 20:49.480
We'll arrest some of
your Brotherhood buddies
and then let you out.

20:49.482 --> 20:51.649
What?
Flynn:
Without charging you.

20:51.651 --> 20:52.950
What do you think Zyklon
would make of that?

20:52.952 --> 20:54.685
Hey, are you trying
to get me killed?

20:54.687 --> 20:56.520
<i> Is that it?</i>

20:56.522 --> 20:57.955
<i> Hey, I just make the meth,</i>
<i> all right? That is all.</i>

20:57.957 --> 20:59.790
These monsters.

20:59.792 --> 21:01.759
What the hell
do they think they're doing?

21:01.761 --> 21:03.094
I don't know,

21:03.096 --> 21:05.696
but this conspiracy is the work
of a highly organized mind.

21:05.698 --> 21:08.399
And I can't see yet
how it was done.

21:08.401 --> 21:12.303
So, if you hear anything
that'll give us a search warrant

21:12.305 --> 21:14.605
for the city block
of apartments

21:14.607 --> 21:17.975
