because I don't work that beat!

21:31.924 --> 21:34.592
But shooting
a deputy D.A...
Jew.

21:34.594 --> 21:36.694
...a court-appointed
attorney...
Mexican.

21:37.463 --> 21:40.031
An LAPD psychologist.

21:40.033 --> 21:41.832
Homo.

21:41.834 --> 21:44.201
An assistant chief
of police.

21:44.203 --> 21:46.270
Black guy.
Come on.

21:46.272 --> 21:47.571
Tao:
The deputy was white.

21:47.573 --> 21:50.408
And Dwight shot him, too.
Explain that.

21:51.177 --> 21:53.577
Dwight shot Simms?

21:54.380 --> 21:56.614
No,
that never happened.

21:56.616 --> 21:58.249
<i> Now you guys</i>
<i> are lying.</i>

21:58.251 --> 21:59.717
He knows Simms.
How?

21:59.719 --> 22:02.153
From jail?

22:02.155 --> 22:04.955
Simms was a trusted lifer
with the sheriff's office,

22:04.957 --> 22:07.591
assigned to high-powered
prisoners like Dwight.

22:07.593 --> 22:10.594
