what happened in the courthouse

23:09.522 --> 23:10.755
some other way.

23:10.757 --> 23:12.490
I suggest you start
with a warrant

23:12.492 --> 23:14.692
and go through every inch
of Deputy Simms' life

23:14.694 --> 23:16.527
and let me know
what you find.

23:16.529 --> 23:18.129
Protection.

23:18.898 --> 23:21.499
