who need protection.

23:21.501 --> 23:24.502
♪♪

23:24.504 --> 23:27.538
Captain,
Simms was law enforcement

23:27.540 --> 23:30.541
<i> and</i> a victim
of this conspiracy?

23:30.543 --> 23:33.244
