Lieutenant.

23:33.246 --> 23:35.446
I think
this is one of those times

23:35.448 --> 23:38.349
when we need
to gather our facts first

23:38.351 --> 23:42.420
and develop
a theory of the crime later.

23:42.422 --> 23:45.456
Dr. Joe:
Sanity is a relative thing.

23:45.458 --> 23:47.158
Dwight wasn't
legally crazy,

23:47.160 --> 23:50.561
