in the back of a police car?

40:01.066 --> 40:03.299
This is an abuse of power
under the color of authority.

40:03.301 --> 40:05.735
Oh, you're gonna take my money
now, too? That's perfect.

40:05.737 --> 40:08.505
Oh, Mike, look who it is --
Mr. Jordan Graff.

40:08.507 --> 40:09.906
Well, Mr. Graff,

40:09.908 --> 40:12.075
we'd be really happy
to hear you make that case.

40:12.077 --> 40:13.910
Why don't you just
step over that way

40:13.912 --> 40:15.478
and answer
a few questions?

40:15.480 --> 40:16.946
We want to tap that brilliant
legal mind of yours.

40:16.948 --> 40:18.782
Violating
my civil rights!

40:18.784 --> 40:20.950
You're violating
my civil rights!
Your civil rights?

40:20.952 --> 40:23.787
I can tell you're a big fan
of civil rights.

40:23.789 --> 40:26.589
LAPD! LAPD!
[ Knock on door ]

40:29.027 --> 40:31.294
Provenza: All right, let's make
sure the building is clear.

40:31.296 --> 40:33.563
Tao: Lieutenant?
Go, Mike.

40:33.565 --> 40:35.398
We found Jordan Graff,

40:35.400 --> 40:37.700
Dwight's fearless leader,
downstairs.

40:37.702 --> 40:40.336
Trying to practice law
without any sense.

40:40.338 --> 40:41.871
Well,
what do you know?

40:41.873 --> 40:44.441
Must have been an attorney,
after all.

40:44.443 --> 40:47.210
See if he can talk himself
into an arrest.

40:47.212 --> 40:48.578
Lieutenant! Lieutenant!

40:48.580 --> 40:49.946
Wait, Mike.
Wait.

40:49.948 --> 40:51.614
I have a feeling
we just found the weapons.

40:51.616 --> 40:55.718
Send SID to the East wing
of the first floor

40:55.720 --> 40:58.288
and have them grab Graff's
prints while you're at it.

40:58.290 --> 41:00.056
Catching a break here.

41:00.058 --> 41:01.891
We're catching a break.

41:01.893 --> 41:06.930
♪♪

41:08.700 --> 41:12.068
That's Hai Sun.
Scratch that, Mike.

41:12.070 --> 41:16.873
Uh, instead of SID,
send Kendall in here right away.

41:16.875 --> 41:19.042
And, uh,
let the captain know

41:19.044 --> 41:22.278
that we have found
our missing court clerk.

41:22.280 --> 41:23.513
[ Cat meows ]

41:23.515 --> 41:27.150
And she can meet her
at the morgue.

41:27.152 --> 41:31.154
[ Radio static ]

41:31.156 --> 41:34.057
♪♪

